OL,3,CDefence begins for man charged with
OL,4,Cserious sexual offences against five
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FThe defence has begun in the trial of
OL,8,Fa man charged with ten charges against
OL,9,Ffive women, including sexual offences,
OL,10,Fone morning in Jersey.
OL,12,FAbdelkarim Arfaoui has pleaded not
OL,13,Fguilty to the charges - which include
OL,14,Fattempted rape, criminal assault, and
OL,15,Fthreatening behaviour.
OL,17,FToday, the court heard his
OL,18,Frecollection of events of the morning
OL,19,Fof 30th November 2025, when the
OL,20,Falleged incidents took place.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
