PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784652479
OL,3,CDefence begins for man charged with
OL,4,Cserious sexual offences against five
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FAided by an interpreter, Arfaoui told
OL,8,Fthe jury that on the night in question
OL,9,Fhe was drunk and lost - and was asking
OL,10,Fthe women for directions as he
OL,11,Fattempted to make his way home.
OL,13,FWhen questioned about one of the
OL,14,Fcharges brought against him, he said
OL,15,Fthere had previously been a consensual
OL,16,Fkiss, but that the victim had grown
OL,17,Fangry with him when he mentioned his
OL,18,Fwife.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784652479
OL,3,CDefence begins for man charged with
OL,4,Cserious sexual offences against five
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FHe added he had to physically restrain
OL,8,Fthe victim when she grew aggressive
OL,9,Fand began to hit him.
OL,11,FWhen asked why he then proceeded to
OL,12,Ffollow her, he explained he had
OL,13,Fsisters and "didn't like" to see women
OL,14,Fupset.
OL,16,FThe court then saw CCTV footage of
OL,17,FArfaoui walking through town between
OL,18,Fthe period of 6 and 7:30am, where he
OL,19,Fapproached the other four women - some
OL,20,Fof whom were on their way home, going
OL,21,Fto work, or going to the gym.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
