OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784652479
OL,3,CDefence begins for man charged with
OL,4,Cserious sexual offences against five
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FOne of the victims was in court and
OL,8,Fbecame visibly emotional as Arfaoui
OL,9,Frecounted his version of events.
OL,11,FHe said he had no sexual intentions
OL,12,Ftowards the women - and was simply
OL,13,Ftrying to ask them for directions home.
OL,15,FWhen questioned about one of the
OL,16,Fvictims who alleges they were
OL,17,Fassaulted, he said it was an accident
OL,18,Fand apologised immediately.
OL,20,FHis trial will continue tomorrow.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
